item.title: CVE-2023-50891|2023-12-29T11:19:01.969Z -- zoho%20forms -- form%20plugin%20for%20wordpress%20%E2%80%93%20zoho%20forms
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in Zoho Forms Form plugin for WordPress – Zoho Forms allows Stored XSS.This issue affects Form plugin for WordPress – Zoho Forms: from n/a through 3.0.1.
